venue.description: Burgers/Breakfast All Day.  Wide variety of delicious vegan/vegetarian alternatives

pageInfo.description:
Diner-style comfort food for vegans, vegetarians, and meat-eaters alike. Burgers, breakfast, and scores of other items available 24 hours a day, 7 days a week.
Gluten-free options available by request.

items.text: The concept joint will serve an ICMB-grade brunch menu up & down the clock. Highlights are some combination of Matzoh Brie, Flapjacks Road Warriors & a chicken-fried bacon cheeseburger.
You'll be like "that wasn't too bad" and you will also be like "why did I eat that"
Heard the vegan mac & cheese balls are IT
This is the worst place I've paid to eat at.
